      "date": "2025-07-01 02:03:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI've disabled the rocky9.5 builds on lustre-reviews now.  They were just enabled on Friday, but I'm not sure why they aren't working.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
