        "subject": "LU-19149 build: make lbuild recognize Rocky Linux",
        "message": "LU-19149 build: make lbuild recognize Rocky Linux\n\nSome Rocky Linux versions return RedHatEnterprise as\na distro name, others return Rocky or RockyLinux.\nMap all these names to \"rhel\" in autodetect_distro().\n\nMake the distro names in autodetect_target() consistently *not*\nhave a dash in them (regardless of how they are specified).\n\nname=$(lsb_release -s -i)\n-> name=RedHatEnterprise\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: bbe5e98180 (\"LU-15874 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.0 5.14.0-70.22.1.el9_0]\")\nFixes: a05d02ea0e (\"LU-16221 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.1 5.14.0-162.12.1.el9_1]\")\nFixes: dd390cd315 (\"LU-16756 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.2 5.14.0-283.el9]\")\nFixes: 9eb87e7ef3 (\"LU-17274 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.3 5.14.0-362.8.1.el9_3]\")\nFixes: 26ef616817 (\"LU-17404 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.4 5.14.0-427.20.1.el9_4]\")\nFixes: 0058de749e (\"LU-18387 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.5 5.14.0-503.14.1.el9_5]\")\nFixes: 4884e85973 (\"LU-18668 kernel: new kernel [RHEL 9.6 5.14.0-570.16.1.el9_6]\")\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I1a626214a1de59fcb0ea4e69826c87742a61c0f0\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/59993\nReviewed-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
